Abstract = {Objective of this work is to propose the right intelligent and
   information model for usage mainly Artificial Intelligence \&
   Operational Research (OR) financial modelling technology as strategic
   part of the Corporate Criminal Intelligence Analysis (CCIA). Providing
   expert operating and strategic capabilities, this technology increases
   the effectiveness, efficiency, and quality of strategic investigative
   operations. Conclusion is that software solution dealing with specific
   Artificial Intelligence \& OR tools must obey specific rules, especially
   in dealing with the criminal incidents, also with the criminals or
   victims, and with the methods employed to control any crime. Now this
   technology (of Information Systems Reengineering) can give us not only
   poor ``ad hoc view{''}, but also new, fast and easy: ``specific crime
   products view{''},{''}specific crime finance view{''}, and ``specific
   regional crime view{''}, in the same time or for various and specific
   periods of time.},
