Abstract = {This paper examines how data mining techniques can assist the monitoring
   of Crime Scene Investigator performance. The findings show that
   Investigators can be placed in one of four groups according to their
   ability to recover DNA and fingerprints from crime scenes. They also
   show that their ability to predict which crime scenes will yield the
