Abstract = {Data mining can be considered as a powerful tool that enables low
   enforcement and emergency agencies to discovery meaningful patterns in a
   large amount of danger situation. In this paper, we propose a data
   mining framework for predicting crimes. The proposed framework consists
   of the following modules: test data generation, classification,
   clustering and data ranking. We performed the experiments using various
   datasets in order to determine which one is potentially best for
   performing crime pattern prediction task.},
