   Laghari, AA (Corresponding Author), Shenyang Normal Univ, Software Coll, Shenyang 110136, Peoples R China.
   Javed, Muhammad; Zhang, Zhaohui, Donghua Univ, Coll Comp Sci, Dept Comp Sci \& Technol, Shanghai 200022, Peoples R China.
