Pages = {61-69},
Month = {JAN},
Abstract = {This paper presents a network evolution model, which is based on the
   clustering approach. The proposed approach depicts the network
   evolution, which demonstrates the network formation from individual
   nodes to fully evolved network. An agglomerative hierarchical clustering
   method is applied for the evolution of network. In the paper, we present
   three case studies which show the evolution of the networks from the
   scratch. These case studies include: terrorist network of 9/11
   incidents, terrorist network of WMD (Weapons Mass Destruction) plot
   against France and a network of tweets discussing a topic. The network
   of 9/11 is also used for evaluation, using other social network analysis
   methods which show that the clusters created using the proposed model of
   network evolution are of good quality, thus the proposed method can be
   used by law enforcement agencies in order to further investigate the
   criminal networks.},
