Number = {12},
Month = {JUN},
Abstract = {Featured Application Machine learning in forensic science and the use of
   MATLAB for identification and classification of petrol source.Abstract
   Petrol is considered the most common fire accelerant. However, the
   identification and classification of petrol sources through the years
   has proven to be a challenging field in the investigation of fire debris
   analysis. This research explored the possibility of identifying petrol
   sources by high-field NMR methods accompanied by ML (machine learning).
   The automated identification and classification of petrol brands were
   achieved for first time based on the ML classification model developed
   in this research. A hierarchical classification model was constructed
   using local classifiers to categorize neat or weathered petrol into its
   sources.},
